Interface VectorOperators.Ternary

All Superinterfaces:
VectorOperators.Operator
Enclosing class:
VectorOperators
public static interface VectorOperators.Ternary extends VectorOperators.Operator
Type for all lane-wise ternary (three-argument) operators, usable in expressions like w = v0.lanewise(FMA, v1, v2).
API Note:
User code should not implement this interface. A future release of this type may restrict implementations to be members of the same package.
